sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant B as Browser (UaClient)
    participant S as OpcUaWsSession
    participant SUB as OpcUaWsSubscription
    participant MI as MonitoredItemService
    participant AS as Address space

    Note over B,S: Implemented in common today: Phase 1 lifecycle message codec<br/>for Create/Modify/Delete subscription + monitored-item requests/responses

    B->>S: CreateSubscriptionRequest<br/>(requestHandle, publishingInterval, keepAlive)
    S->>SUB: create subscription (id=N)
    S-->>B: CreateSubscriptionResponse (id=N)

    B->>S: CreateMonitoredItemsRequest<br/>(requestHandle, subId=N, NodeId[], samplingInterval)
    S->>MI: CreateMonitoredItems
    MI->>AS: attach adapter per item
    AS-->>MI: initial DataValue[]
    MI-->>SUB: queue initial values
    MI-->>S: monitoredItemId[]
    S-->>B: CreateMonitoredItemsResponse

    B->>S: ModifySubscription / SetPublishingMode / SetMonitoringMode
    S-->>B: matching response envelopes
    B->>S: ModifyMonitoredItems / DeleteMonitoredItems / DeleteSubscriptions
    S-->>B: matching response envelopes

    Note over B,SUB: Pending runtime work: websocket session loop, Publish/Republish,<br/>TransferSubscriptions, keep-alive timers, and queued notification replay

    loop Publish pump
        B->>S: PublishRequest (acks for prior seq)
        alt data-change available
            SUB-->>S: NotificationMessage (changes)
            S-->>B: PublishResponse (seq, notifications)
        else no data, keep-alive tick
            S-->>B: PublishResponse (keep-alive, no notifications)
        end
    end

    Note over B,S: Connection drops, browser reconnects

    B->>S: TransferSubscriptionsRequest(subId=N)
    alt session still alive
        S-->>B: Good, subscription transferred
    else session expired
        S-->>B: BadSessionIdInvalid
        B->>S: CreateSubscription + CreateMonitoredItems (resume)
    end

    B->>S: RepublishRequest(subId=N, seq=last_acked+1)
    S-->>B: PublishResponse (replayed)
